      CHPWHTotTankVol           Central HPWH primary tank volume (total across all tanks)     Float         -  -  -   Units: gal                Optional input     
      CHPWHTankCount            Number of central HPWH storage tanks                          Integer       -  -  -    -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -   Optional input     
      CHPWHTankRVal             Central HPWH storage tank insulation R-value                  Float         -  -  -   Units: °F-ft2-h/Btu       Optional input     
      CHPWHTankLoc              location of central primary DHW tank(s)                       Enumeration   -  -  -    -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -   Optional input     
                                      default:  0
                                            0:  "- select tank location -"
                                            1:  "Outside"
                                            2:  "Zone"

                               ResGarage
                               ResZn
                               ResAttic
                               ResCrawlSpc
                               ResOtherZn

                                      default:  0

                                            1:  "Outside"
                                            2:  "Zone"

                                      default:  0
                                            0:  "None (return to Primary)"

                                            2:  "Parallel"
      CHPWHLoopTankType         type of central HPWH secondary tank                           Enumeration   -  -  -    -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -   Optional input     
                               When:  ResDHWSys:CHPWHSysDescrip = "Integrated/Packaged System"
                                      default:  1
                                            1:  "Electric Resistance"
                                            2:  "Integrated/Packaged System"
                               When:  ResDHWSys:CHPWHSysDescrip = "Single Pass Primary"
                                      default:  1
                                            1:  "Electric Resistance"
                                            2:  "Integrated/Packaged System"
                                           10:  "Single Pass Primary"
                                           11:  "Multi Pass Primary"
                               When:  ResDHWSys:CHPWHSysDescrip = "Multi Pass Primary"
                                      default:  1
                                            1:  "Electric Resistance"
                                            2:  "Integrated/Packaged System"
                                           10:  "Single Pass Primary"
                                           11:  "Multi Pass Primary"
                               else:
                                      default:  1
                                            1:  "Electric Resistance"
